episodes.title: I Grew Up In A Religious Ballet Cult 😱🩰
episodes.description:
Hi! This is my life story about the time I was in a toxic religious ballet academy.

I speak a bit about my Vaganova ballet dancing background, And give some insight on what it’s actually like to train as a professional ballet dancer. 🩰


Follow me on IG!
